data.description: This charming 2-story home, nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, features 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage. Recent upgrades include new carpet and fresh paint throughout, along with beautifully landscaped front and back yards. The kitchen comes complete with all appliances, and the primary bedroom boasts a spacious closet, a garden tub, double sinks, and a separate shower. The generous living space includes a cozy gas fireplace and a dining area, while a large laundry room, pantry, and extra storage add to the convenience of this lovely home.
